channel.title: How do I make it so you cannot teleport out of jail
channel.description: When I jail people for breaking the rules they can just teleport out of jail!!! Is there a way I could put a tele-Block on people that are in jail? Thanks if you can help me out!

item.title: How do I make it so you cannot teleport out of jail
item.dc:creator: @ChaosPkers ChaosPkers
item.description:
@ChaosPkers wrote:

just put under your command

teleblock = true;
